Implementasi Firebase Firestore pada Aplikasi Cepu
1. Install depedensi : cloud_firestore, image_picker, geolocator, url_launcher
2. Buat model post.dart di folder models, dgn property:
id, image, description,, category, latitude, longitude, user_id, user_fullname

3. Buat service post_service.dart di folder services
4. Buat screen : add_post_screen.dart dan detail_screen.dart
5. Tambahkan floating action button di home screen ke halaman AddPostScreen